haracteristics." O 0[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[7] Nesher G, Mates M, Zevin S "Effect of caffeine consumption on efficacy of methotrexate in rheumatoid arthritis." Arthritis Rheum 48 (2003): 571-572', 1767365206);
